🌲🌀 Cursed Canopy VR 🕷️ – Long Description

Venture deep into the Cursed Canopy, a mysterious jungle shrouded in darkness and legend. 🌿✨ In this Gorilla Tag fangame, you’ll use your hands and instincts to climb, swing, and leap through a haunted forest where every sound and shadow feels alive. 👀🌒

Explore towering trees wrapped in twisted vines, ancient ruins lost to time, and glowing spirits that drift between the branches. 💀👻 Each area holds hidden secrets and unexpected dangers — only the brave will uncover what lies beyond the fog. 🌫️🔥

Challenge your speed, reflexes, and courage as you navigate an environment that changes when you least expect it. 🕸️ Whether you’re racing through the treetops or exploring the cursed depths, every movement brings you closer to uncovering the truth behind the canopy’s curse. 🌲💫

Do you have what it takes to survive the forest’s grip… or will you become one of its lost echoes? 🌀🌙
